==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: File closer
<hw>File" clos`er</hw>. <fld>(Mil.)</fld> <def>A commissioned or
noncommissioned officer posted in the rear of a line, or on the flank of
a column, of soldiers, to rectify mistakes and insure steadiness and
promptness in the ranks.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

